Directory layout
================

common:
  config:         shared settings for the whole system
  lib:            shared lib files among "master" & "worker"
flex_ui:          Nova's user interface implemented in Flex
flex_vnc:         [incubation] VNC viewer in Flex, will be merged into flex_ui in future
master:           "master" module of Nova system
scripts:          some helper scripts, including install.sh
tools:
  linux_agent:    Linux guest OS configuration utilities
  server_side:    helper tools for "master" & "worker" modules
  win_agent:      Windows guest OS configuration utilities

